```plantuml
@startuml jes_autopatzer

actor User
participant "React UI" as UI
participant "Electron App" as Electron
participant "Lichess API" as Lichess
participant "Arduino (Teensy)" as Teensy
participant "Perl Script" as Perl
participant "Stepper Motor Driver" as Motor
participant "Hall Effect Sensors" as Sensors
participant "CD4051B Multiplexer" as Multiplexer

User -> UI: Open App
UI -> Electron: Initialize
Electron -> Lichess: Connect WebSocket
Lichess --> Electron: Connection Established

User -> UI: Start Game
UI -> Electron: Fetch Board State
Electron -> Lichess: Request Game State
Lichess --> Electron: Deliver Game State
Electron -> Perl: Process Game Data

Perl -> Teensy: Send Movement Commands
Teensy -> Motor: Move Piece
Motor -> Sensors: Check Position
Sensors -> Multiplexer: Send Sensor Data
Multiplexer -> Teensy: Relay Sensor Data

Teensy -> Perl: Report Piece Position
Perl -> UI: Update Board State
UI -> User: Display Updated Board

User -> UI: Make Move
UI -> Electron: Validate Move
Electron -> Lichess: Send Move
Lichess --> Electron: Confirm Move
Electron -> Perl: Communicate Move

Perl -> Teensy: Execute Move
Teensy -> Motor: Move Piece
Motor -> Sensors: Check Position
Sensors -> Multiplexer: Send Sensor Data
Multiplexer -> Teensy: Relay Sensor Data
Teensy -> Perl: Confirm Position
Perl -> UI: Update Board
UI -> User: Show Move Confirmation

@enduml
```